      <title>政治风险抑制泰国债券市场，令全球基金保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/political-risks-stifle-thai-bonds-keeping-global-funds-wary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国的一系列政治风险让外国投资者对该国债券保持谨慎，尽管他们在五月份六个月来首次小心翼翼地重返市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-06/political-risks-stifle-thai-bonds-keeping-global-funds-wary</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Jun 2024 00:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
